ut-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Solar-Powered Cabana Platform<\/p>\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-xl\">Grow Premium Seating Revenue Across Resorts and Waterparks<\/h1>\n<p class=\"lg9-copy\">Built for operations managers and commercial decision makers, LounGenie improves guest flow, speeds poolside service, and helps premium seating deliver stronger daily revenue.<\/p>\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons lg9-cta-row is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button lg9-btn-primary\" href=\"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/contact-loungenie\/\">Book a Property Demo<\/a><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button lg9-btn-secondary\" href=\"https:\/\/loungenie.com\/staging\/poolside-amenity-unit\/\">See Platform Features<\/a><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"lg9-stat-row\"><div class=\"lg9-stat\"><strong>Resorts<\/strong><span>Premium seating that supports higher-value guest stays and longer dwell time.<\/span><\/div><div class=\"lg9-stat\"><strong>Waterparks<\/strong><span>Pool deck operations with faster service flow and less guest friction.<\/span><\/div><div class=\"lg9-stat\"><strong>Operations Teams<\/strong><span>A cleaner path from guest intent to staff action in premium seating zones.<\/span><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id-lg-home-proof lg9-section\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-row kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row kt-inner-column-height-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-shell has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Why Operators Take The Meeting<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-md\">A rollout model built to remove adoption friction, not add it.<\/h2>\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns lg9-grid-3 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card lg9-card-soft is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">$0 upfront deployment<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">The commercial model lowers the barrier to testing premium seating performance at the property level.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card lg9-card-soft is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">PoolSafe handles service<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">Installation, maintenance, and service stay with PoolSafe so the venue team is not left managing hardware support.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card lg9-card-soft is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Built for premium seating economics<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">LounGenie is designed to improve comfort, capture purchase intent, and strengthen the revenue value of cabanas and daybeds.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id-lg-home-value lg9-section lg9-soft\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-row kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row kt-inner-column-height-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-shell has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Why It Matters<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-md\">One platform that improves guest experience, operations, and revenue.<\/h2>\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns lg9-grid-3 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card lg9-card-soft is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Guest Experience<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">Give guests secure storage, charging, and smoother service interactions without leaving premium seating.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card lg9-card-soft is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Operational Efficiency<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">Reduce service friction with clearer guest requests and faster ordering flow from cabana and daybed zones.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card lg9-card-soft is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Commercial Performance<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">Capture more purchase intent and increase dwell time in high-value pool deck seating.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id-lg-home-commercial lg9-section\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-row kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row kt-inner-column-height-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-shell has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Commercial Model<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-md\">A platform that aligns guest comfort, service workflow, and commercial upside.<\/h2><p class=\"lg9-copy\">LounGenie helps properties upgrade the premium seating experience without asking operators to bolt together multiple guest-facing tools, service workflows, and hardware relationships on their own.<\/p><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">What operators evaluate first<\/h3><ul style=\"margin:16px 0 0;padding-left:20px;color:#466170;line-height:1.75;\"><li>No upfront rollout cost<\/li><li>PoolSafe installation, maintenance, and service<\/li><li>Classic, Service+, and 2.0 tiers that build on each other<\/li><li>Brand customization for towels, cabanas, lounge chairs, and seating zones<\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id-lg-home-core lg9-section lg9-soft\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-row kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row kt-inner-column-height-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-shell has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Core Functions<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-md\">Order, stash, charge, and chill in one premium-seat experience.<\/h2>\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns lg9-grid-3 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Order<\/p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Capture intent at the seat.<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">QR ordering keeps the transaction path close to the guest and shortens the time between intent and purchase.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Stash<\/p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Protect valuables poolside.<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">Waterproof secure storage improves comfort and supports longer stays in premium areas.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Charge<\/p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Keep devices powered and guests present.<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">Solar USB charging reduces drop-off caused by dead phones and supports all-day engagement.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Chill<\/p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Make every premium seat feel fully considered.<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">A removable ice bucket completes the premium hospitality experience and reinforces seat value.<\/p><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id-lg-home-installations 